The protein can be saved as a mol2 file using Chimera
The protein surface can be dumped (in dms format) using Chimera.
The sample ligand used here must already be in place. It will determine the docking site

This directory contains files related to sphere generation.

                             --- * ---

script_demo          script to automatically perform demonstration
rec.ms               molecular surface of protein (generated using "dms")
INSPH                SPHGEN input file
sphgen_cluster.in    SHOWSPHERE input file for largest cluster created by sphgen
selected_spheres.in  SHOWSPHERE input file for spheres within 10 Ang of ligand
script_clean         script to remove files made by script_demo
